# Terraform working files — never commit these.
**/.terraform/*
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.*
crash.log
crash.*.log
override.tf
override.tf.json
*_override.tf
*_override.tf.json
.terraformrc
terraform.rc
plan.out
plan.json

# NOTE: *.tfvars is intentionally NOT ignored here — the .tfvars files in these
# chapters are example teaching artifacts and contain no secrets. In a real
# project you would ignore *.tfvars / *.auto.tfvars to avoid committing secrets.
